Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Throne of Roses.III Lord of Abyss
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吗 修女?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 圣下呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么我能帮上忙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你暂时在这边休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 一定能找回圣下的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、虽然我什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过、大声叫嚷和使用暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没办法把想法传达的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要教训我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 由于我什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这里…一直有人被关着这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、我想多知道一些 你们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从圣下身边给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布拉德·佩卓斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下赶来救您了 圣下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱拐圣下的贵体 谋划叛乱祖国 简直天理难容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地与我铁锤上的露水一同消散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神罚!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在说什么 圣下?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还曾经想夺取您的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人…只是被关着 没有生存空间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 不要杀她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听听他们 听听他们想说的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要放过叛乱的主谋者吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是阿尔比恩国内的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管皇宫中发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责任都在阿尔比恩身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也这么说过吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是吸血鬼是我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副局长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有一个男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这个男子汉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我当做一位骑士来恳求我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果拒绝他的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不再是骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就不配当一个侍奉神的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布拉德·佩卓斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不杀我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费我这么多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这里也遇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些「自动化猎兵」们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是低级的趣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有「骑士团」会使用这种手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣下呢 没到你那边去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从他们介入的情况看来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能再继续拖延了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经跟你说过多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不明白吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥总是说再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但光是等待…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会有什么改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为发动叛乱 能有什么改变吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来 不论短生种还是长生种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都缩在自己的壳里 将视线从对方的身上移开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有少数 但是能看清真实的世代已经诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多奇怪的士兵侵入进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在进行无差别的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什、什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居住区没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把监视器切换过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡妮莎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三势力 …
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不站住的话 就要开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还没完全恢复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊萨克真是的 不好好修理的话会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:13:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…究竟是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去 修女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到了 圣下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副局长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣下 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 佩卓斯 佩卓…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 电梯
